RAWALPINDI, Sep 19 (APP): A Pakistan Armed Forces contingent on Saturday participated in the opening ceremony of multinational military exercise Kavkaz 2020, held at Astrakhan region, Russia.
The multimilitary Exercise Kavkaz (21-26 Sep) aimed at assessing ability of troops to react to various challenges and learn from each otherâ€™s experiences, said an ISPR press release.
